  "title": {
    "rendered": "Contact LounGenie | Request a Demo for Your Property"
  },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "\r\n<div class=\"lg-master-shell is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\r\n  <!-- Global header block (inline safe header) -->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"lg-global-header is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 24px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#041224,#0a315f);\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\r\n    <div class=\"lg-logo\" style=\"flex:0 0 auto;\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/lg-logo-white.png\" alt=\"LounGenie logo\" style=\"height:44px;\"/></div>\r\n    <nav class=\"lg-nav\" style=\"flex:1 1 auto;text-align:center;font-weight:800;color:#fff;\">\r\n      <a href=\"/staging/\" style=\"color:#fff;margin:0 14px;\">Products</a>\r\n      <a href=\"/staging/cabana-installation-photos/\" style=\"color:#fff;margin:0 14px;\">Gallery</a>\r\n      <a href=\"/staging/investors/\" style=\"color:#fff;margin:0 14px;\">Investors</a>\r\n      <a href=\"/staging/contact/\" style=\"color:#fff;margin:0 14px;\">Contact</a>\r\n    </nav>\r\n    <div class=\"lg-cta\" style=\"flex:0 0 auto;\"><a href=\"/staging/contact/\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0050a8,#00a9dd);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;color:#fff;font-weight:800;\">Request Demo</a></div>\r\n  </div></div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  <!-- Hero: Deep Blue gradient, bold title -->\r\n  <style>#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{align-content:start;}:where(#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap) > .wp-block-kadence-column{justify-content:start;}#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{column-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);row-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);padding-top:var( --global-kb-row-default-top, 25px );padding-bottom:var( --global-kb-row-default-bottom, 25px );padding-top:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-bottom:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-layout-overlay{opacity:0.30;}@media all and (max-width: 1024px){#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}}@media all and (max-width: 767px){#kt-layout-idmaster_hero_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1fr);}}</style>\r\n  <div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap\">\r\n    <div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\r\n      <h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">LounGenie — Hospitality Technology for Premium Seating</h1>\r\n      <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0;max-width:820px;\">High-energy, guest-first amenity solutions: waterproof safe, solar USB charging, QR ordering, and service call support — designed for cabanas, daybeds and premium seating.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  <!-- Feature Carousel (static fallback markup using Kadence/columns) -->\r\n  <style>#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{align-content:start;}:where(#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap) > .wp-block-kadence-column{justify-content:start;}#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{column-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);row-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);padding-top:var( --global-kb-row-default-top, 25px );padding-bottom:var( --global-kb-row-default-bottom, 25px );padding-top:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-bottom:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-layout-overlay{opacity:0.30;}@media all and (max-width: 1024px){#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}}@media all and (max-width: 767px){#kt-layout-idmaster_carousel_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1fr);}}</style>\r\n  <div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap\">\r\n    <div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\r\n      <!-- Carousel: three feature cards -->\r\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;\">\r\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:18px;min-width:260px;max-width:360px;text-align:left;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"color:#fff;margin-top:0;\">QR Ordering</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0\">Guests scan a QR and orders print on the dedicated staff printer — no POS integration required.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:18px;min-width:260px;max-width:360px;text-align:left;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"color:#fff;margin-top:0;\">Waterproof Safe</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0\">Waterproof safe with keypad for guest valuables — secure and accessible.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:18px;min-width:260px;max-width:360px;text-align:left;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"color:#fff;margin-top:0;\">Solar USB Charging</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0\">Integrated solar USB ports to keep guests powered throughout the day.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  <!-- Bento Grid: Asymmetrical tech specs -->\r\n  <style>#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{align-content:start;}:where(#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap) > .wp-block-kadence-column{justify-content:start;}#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{column-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);row-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-md, 2rem);padding-top:var( --global-kb-row-default-top, 25px );padding-bottom:var( --global-kb-row-default-bottom, 25px );padding-top:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-bottom:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-layout-overlay{opacity:0.30;}@media all and (max-width: 1024px){#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));}}@media all and (max-width: 767px){#kt-layout-idmaster_bento_$PageId > .kt-row-column-wrap{grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1fr);}}</style>\r\n  <div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap\">\r\n    <div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\r\n      <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);padding:20px;border-radius:12px;color:#fff;\">\r\n          <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Dimensions</h4>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0;margin:0;\">Custom-fit to seat pockets and cabana rails.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"grid-column:span 2;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);padding:20px;border-radius:12px;color:#fff;\">\r\n          <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Features</h4>\r\n          <ul style=\"color:#e0e0e0;margin:0;padding-left:18px;\"><li>QR Ordering (prints to staff printer)</li><li>Waterproof safe</li><li>Solar USB charging</li></ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);padding:20px;border-radius:12px;color:#fff;\">\r\n          <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Materials</h4>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0;margin:0;\">Commercial-grade aluminum interior; waterproof keypad.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  <!-- Footer: 4-column corporate footer with TSXV ticker -->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"lg-master-footer is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg,#081624,#0f4a86);color:#fff;padding:44px 24px;margin-top:32px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\r\n    <div style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px;\">\r\n      <div>\r\n        <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Product</h4>\r\n        <ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;color:#e0e0e0;\"><li>Cabana Units</li><li>Service+</li></ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Company</h4>\r\n        <ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;color:#e0e0e0;\"><li>About</li><li>Careers</li></ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Resources</h4>\r\n        <ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;color:#e0e0e0;\"><li>Gallery</li><li>Press</li></ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">Investor</h4>\r\n        <p style=\"color:#e0e0e0;margin:0;\">TSXV: POOL</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div></div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n",
    "protected": false
  },
  "excerpt": {
    "rendered": "<p>Contact LounGenie to request a demo and evaluate fit for hotels, resorts, and waterparks looking to improve premium seating revenue.</p>\n",
